{
  "text": "ROC analyses were performed on signature expression scores that summarize, for each sample, the expression level of all the genes in a predictive gene set [CITATION_1] . Given a gene expression dataset (including data adjusted for proportion variations) and a gene signature/set, the signature score S j for sample j was computed as:",
